{"type": "article", "id": 61586, "title": "苹果 iPhone 摄影赛选出第五届获奖作品，星巴克将在天猫补货“猫爪杯” | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-02-27T07:22:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 8530, "name": "樱花"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190227125709Ru49irTtnVJWGDsY.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"558F\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BuURcmpBo_Q/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tommy Haas 成为 Fila 品牌形象代言人。</b></a>他作为一名德国男子职业网球选手，职业生涯的最高排名曾达到第 2 位。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125806W36gSC78rtmwXnqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.993773\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"5e8W\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1763527064/4343935831342251\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>王俊凯代言宝洁旗下衣物洗护品牌碧浪，</b></a>同时在京东开启“王俊凯的阳光味道”促销活动。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125829JWUhc3te6xfqsSMB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561622\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"0bCC\"><b><a href=\"https://www.hmv.co.jp/artist_%E3%82%B9%E3%83%BC%E3%83%91%E3%83%BC%E3%83%9E%E3%83%AA%E3%82%AA_000000000751117/item_%E3%82%B9%E3%83%BC%E3%83%91%E3%83%BC%E3%83%9E%E3%83%AA%E3%82%AA-%E3%81%97%E3%82%87%E3%81%86%E3%82%86%E7%9A%BF-%E3%83%9E%E3%83%AA%E3%82%AA_9661783\" rel=\"nofollow\">任天堂将在日本发售主“超级马里奥”主题的酱油蘸碟，</a></b>碟底分别是超级马里奥、无敌星星和火花图案。调料注入的时候，图案也慢慢呈现出来。定价为 864 日元，将于 4 月 28 日在 HMV 上发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125846621UAxojMT309w7V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629229\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125846E5VbQjBwGazI0C3p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125846QxPlf5GzgC4I0F83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125846YMZ23Xk8prSvzsPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"LSRH\"><a href=\"https://v.lpiii.cn/nqxx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>腾讯视频的网剧《怒晴湘西》，联合三星堆博物馆、金沙遗址博物馆发布了名为“修复文物 遇见文明”的 H5。</b></a>里面呈现的三款文物需要参与者完成修复，让用户在剧情之外再次体验文物的珍贵。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902271259106iuH7jKON4knX3Bh.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.779412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125910ZqYwVBshJ03TiDRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.605333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125910LkedKfDlwC5gV8H2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.026667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"Lw94\">星巴克昨天发售了樱花系列周边新品，其中容量 6 盎司的“猫爪杯”成为网红商品遭到抢售。搭配小猫玩偶杯垫的整套定价为 199 元，而淘宝转卖售价高达 700 元。<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4343980429357750?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>星巴克昨天下午宣布正在安排补货，并且将在天猫星巴克官方旗舰店上架。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019022712592965IbpisaPXyVEdlm.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227125929OqNjK0ZWtJshDba1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"wWEm\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwOTA2MzYwNA==&amp;mid=2247486827&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=dc5b4b8fb1b25a4c3ef13f577f783a52&amp;chksm=9778d6b0a00f5fa68a2b9f51b061f9877b10a27bf7c88dc1cb0462942b4699db056221691337&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0226hK7xlmgsQLxXm1hw35mr&amp;key=e26fe09897582c583044b8fc3561864b272727cea3ea9005e9c0ec21e6fbd41c39ac39744f8780e782b258307dc71dd1279abe023a4fd077fdbad1490de29d3e02887b4d2980a3ac03a4ed5c8fcf11e8&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=7AUymKJqXgKZJH85YrBN8gu0zK70pyb3jJuEvHKsnI%2FK9WDQV3ylVam8klQ4MAXk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>苹果面向全球举办的 ”Shot on iPhone“ 活动评选出 10 幅作品。</b></a>评审团包括中国摄影师陈漫，前白宫官方摄影师 Pete Souza，并对获选作品做了点评。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130000va1d0WbFQKHw2kpR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799020\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\"><p>用 iPhone XS Max 拍摄 | Alex Jiang</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130000kXY0Vq2bsMcD4xrB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\"><p>用 iPhone XS Max 拍摄 | Blake Marvin</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130000kXc86GnxsBWj7hu4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\"><p>用 iPhone XS Max 拍摄 | Darren Soh&nbsp;</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130000idGEbp513jCghFuc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332108\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\"><p>用 iPhone X 拍摄 | Dina Alfasi</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130000WEv3KpCGBae1xjlw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\"><p>用 iPhone 8 Plus 拍摄 | Elizabeth Scarrott</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902271300018MsgpDPd7hHC3Z9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\"><p>用 iPhone 7 拍摄 | Nikita Yarosh</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902271300011zyk9IPm7DSYdWRL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\"><p>用 iPhone XS 拍摄 | Andrew Griswold</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130001W9d7wHMcItDTK3AR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248775\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">用 iPhone XS Max 拍摄 | Bernard Antolin</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130021MBiYrPy0uaznHjJv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">用 iPhone XS 拍摄 | LieAdi Darmawan&nbsp;</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190227130002XYv6s97aPWHliCu5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">用 iPhone 7 拍摄 | Robert Glasser&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><p line=\"JMSh\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g74sc4O8vqg&amp;t=5s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国大麻零售商 MedMen 为大麻规范使用拍了支广告 <em>The New Normal。</em></b></a>片中从大麻的历史讲起，陆续展现了由于错误使用大麻导致的结果。电影 <em>Her</em> 的导演斯派克·琼斯，美剧《实习医生格蕾》中的演员杰西·威廉姆斯也都有出镜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l0842kkwqj3\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t</div><p line=\"s8OU\"><b><a href=\"https://www.newbalance.co.uk/bnr-strava-runaway-pub.html?awc=6533_1551232356_c5785561cffeb578a708e8b8d36c0378&amp;utm_source=awin&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=adgoal+GmbH+-+Content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">New Balance 在伦敦的查令十字街上开了第一家酒吧 ”The Runaway“</a>。</b>不过消费者在这家酒吧使用的货币是跑步英里数，而非英镑。New Balance 和测速应用 Strava 合作围绕马拉松训练推出四项挑战赛，参加者跑步的里程数，来兑换能喝多少品脱的啤酒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902271301032hUfIygsqQuZN8r5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"aUI3\"><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/agency-news/ikea-taps-work-digital-product-partner/316760/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宜家最近宣布数字产品代理公司 Work＆Co 将负责数字产品业务。</b></a>它将协助提升宜家的电商、移动端和线下购物参与度。代理商将整合战略，制定长期的解决方案。</p><p line=\"8Y3z\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/cannes-lions-parent-company-ascential-looks-to-rebuild-after-revenue-dip-due-to-publicis-boycott/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>戛纳广告节母公司 Ascential 发布 2018 年财报，营销部门包括戛纳广告节和咨询公司 MediaLink 的总收入下降。</b></a>公司整体有机增长为 6.3%，但是营销部门的有机收入减少了 1200 万美元，其中戛纳广告节下降了 8%。这可能与去年的参与人数下降了 20% - 25% 有关。</p><p line=\"8Y3z\"><br></p><p line=\"nlPw\">题图来自：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/XWBDwXcgIxo?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brendan Church</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/iphone-photo?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}